Title: An Act Changing the Name of Balasiao Elementary School in the Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Isabelo Calma, Sr. Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 812
An Act Changing the Name of Balasiao Elementary School in the Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Isabelo Calma, Sr. Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Balasiao Elementary School, in Barangay Balasiao, Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Isabelo Calma, Sr. Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
